metadata.name: Shut Up I Am Dreaming
metadata.description:
As the sun began to set over the horizon, a young girl lay peacefully on the sandy beach, her skin caressed by the gentle ebb and flow of the waves. With each passing moment, she sank deeper into a state of blissful slumber, lost in the soothing rhythm of the sea and the soft rustle of the breeze. As the world around her faded into a haze of warmth and contentment, she knew that this moment would stay with her always, a cherished memory of a tranquil moment in time.
